event.title: RustWeek
event.metaDesc: A full week of Rust, including a maintainer event and Rusts 10 year birthday
event.content: RustWeek is May 13â€“17, in Utrecht, the Netherlands - with two days of talks, one day of workshops, sponsor and interaction space to talk and connect, and social activities all-week. This year will include Rust's 10th birthday celebration, an unconference for maintainers, and the first official Rust All Hands since 2019!
